# Web3Forms – free contact form delivery
# 1. Visit https://web3forms.com/
# 2. Enter your email address → they send you an access key instantly (no account needed)
# 3. Copy the key here
# 4. Rename this file to .env.local  (already in .gitignore so it stays off Git)
# 5. Add the same variable to your Vercel project:
#    Vercel dashboard → project → Settings → Environment Variables

NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your_access_key_here
